reviews.comment: Yep. All chargers marked out of service.
All spots in use. But to make it worse, two spots are used by Chevy sparks that are totally charged but other two are iced.  So 4 spots and no one is charging.

Nice and shaded in parking garage. I got the last of 4 spots. None of the other 3 cars were checked in, but in thier defense, there is no sign asking to check in with the app like most of the other evolve chargers. Should there be?

Read volt not checked in. And white Nissan iced one spot. Spaces could use painting when warmer weather gets here to show reserved.

1 spot already ICE,d by white Nissan SUV. Hopefully marking the floor will help when it warms up.
